title: Test `run-pass/command-uid-gid.rs` fails on emscripten

labels.name: A-testsuite
labels.description: Area: The testsuite used to check the correctness of rustc

body:
Due to a regression in `compiletest` some `run-pass` tests weren't run properly for some time and this is one of the regressions that slipped through during that time.

https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/62797#issuecomment-513428569
```
2019-07-20T02:37:15.4921233Z ---- [run-pass] run-pass/command-uid-gid.rs stdout ----

2019-07-20T02:37:15.4921438Z status: exit code: 101
2019-07-20T02:37:15.4921776Z command: "/emsdk-portable/node/8.9.1_64bit/bin/node" "/checkout/obj/build/x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu/test/run-pass/command-uid-gid/a.js"
2019-07-20T02:37:15.4921863Z stdout:
2019-07-20T02:37:15.4922083Z ------------------------------------------
```
